        Pricing Psychology and Anchoring for Brisbane Sellers
      </h1>
      <p style="font-size:1rem;color:rgba(240,236,228,0.6);line-height:1.8;max-width:54ch;">
        The first number a buyer sees becomes their reference point. Every price they encounter afterwards is judged against it. For Brisbane sellers, understanding how that anchor works is the difference between a campaign that builds momentum and one that stalls.
      </p>
